ic Debt. 6. You MUST include a section exactly titled 'Next Step:' suggesting an architectural pattern for robustness in Python (e.g., robust try/except handling, logging, custom exceptions, or task queues). | [EXPLANATION GATE & SCROLL BARRIER] After Phase 1, you MUST insert exactly this visual separator:
